Content:
Just looking at the weather forecast and they are predicting some snow
for this coming weekend.
So...I did the only thing I could do.
I went out for a short ride around the area, then
I put the Goldwing away in my heated workshop for the winter.
Boo hoo hoo! It's over 'til April!!
What will I ever do with myself for the next three months?
